### 1. Registrar usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Juan",
  "email": "juan@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Login — copia el token de la respuesta
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "juan@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Crear tarea — pega tu token aquí
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "title": "Aprender Docker",
  "description": "Completar el proyecto TaskFlow",
  "userId": 1
}

### 4. Ver tareas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?userId=1
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 5. Intentar sin token — debe dar 401
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks